Class Name: RoosterFactory
Language: Java

Description:

The RoosterFactory class implements the Factory Design Pattern to create instances of different rooster types in the Cock Clashers game. It centralizes the creation logic for Rooster objects, allowing for custom names, random selection, or specific type selection. This approach promotes modularity and scalability when adding new rooster types.

Key Features:

Creates specific rooster types based on player choice.

Supports custom naming of roosters.

Can generate a random rooster for AI opponents or gameplay variety.

Ensures default fallback if an invalid choice is provided.


Methods:

public static Rooster createRooster(int choice, String customName)

